Class KeyValues

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.jadler.KeyValues

  • public class KeyValues
extends Object

    This class represents a key-value data structure with following features:

    • multiple values for one key
    • key case insensitivity
    • immutability

    This structure is used in Jadler for modeling request/response headers and request parameters.

    Please note this class is immutable and therefore thread safe. All addition operations (add(java.lang.String, java.lang.String), addAll(net.jadler.KeyValues) create new instances rather than modifying the instance.
